Create XLD package and Version - ET
tasks.script:
if releaseVariables['XLD_PACKAGE_PV_ET'] != 'null':
   aid_dar = releaseVariables['ARTIFACTID_DAR']
   XLD_PACKAGE_PV_ET = releaseVariables['XLD_PACKAGE_PV_ET']
   XLD_PACKAGE_PV_ET = reduce(lambda s, pat: s.split(pat, 1)[1], 'Applications' + '/', XLD_PACKAGE_PV_ET)
   releaseVariables['XLD_PACKAGE_PV_ET'] = XLD_PACKAGE_PV_ET
   VERSION_PV_ET = releaseVariables['XLD_PACKAGE_PV_ET']
   VERSION_PV_ET = reduce(lambda s, pat: s.split(pat, 1)[1], aid_dar + '/', VERSION_PV_ET)
   releaseVariables['VERSION_PV_ET'] = VERSION_PV_ET

tasks.title: Create XLD package and Version - PR
tasks.script:
if releaseVariables['XLD_PACKAGE_PV_PR'] != 'null':   
   aid_dar = releaseVariables['ARTIFACTID_DAR']
   XLD_PACKAGE_PV_PR = releaseVariables['XLD_PACKAGE_PV_PR']
   XLD_PACKAGE_PV_PR = reduce(lambda s, pat: s.split(pat, 1)[1], 'Applications' + '/', XLD_PACKAGE_PV_PR)
   releaseVariables['XLD_PACKAGE_PV_PR'] = XLD_PACKAGE_PV_PR

   VERSION_PV_PR = releaseVariables['XLD_PACKAGE_PV_PR']
   VERSION_PV_PR = reduce(lambda s, pat: s.split(pat, 1)[1], aid_dar + '/', VERSION_PV_PR)
   releaseVariables['VERSION_PV_PR'] = VERSION_PV_PR
